========
 POPCON 
========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Wijnand 'tehmaze' Modderman - http://tehmaze.com
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license:  BSD
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

gozerbots popularity contest at http://plugins.gozerbot.org/popcon/

| 

  enlists your bot in the popularity contest page at %s (if enabled with 
  popcon-enable)
 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *popcon*

    :description: show whether the bot is participating in the popcon

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !popcon
        <output> bot is not participating in the popularity contest,
        <output>  use popcon-enable to enable it


2) *popcon-cfg*

    :description: plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !popcon-cfg
        <output> options: bot-id="" .. enabled=False .. url="http://plugins.gozerbot.org/popcon/"
        <output>  .. version="GOZERBOT 0.9"


3) *popcon-cfgsave*

    :description: save plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !popcon-cfgsave
        <output> config saved


4) *popcon-enable*

    :description: join the popularity contest

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !popcon-enable
        <output> ok


5) *popcon-update*

    :description: update bots popcon data

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !popcon-update
        <output> bot is not participating in the popularity contest,
        <output>  use popcon-enable to enable it


6) *popcon-url*

    :description: shows your bot's entry in the popularity contest (if enabled)

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !popcon-url
        <output> none
